1236:				;
1237:				; *** Surface scan ***
1238:				; Read every block to ensure that they are readable. The reserved (system) area
1239:				; is not read, as this may have a different geometry to the files area and this
1240:				; may cause trouble. Blocks extend from 0 (the beginning of the directory) to
1241:				; DPB.DSM. Each block consists of DPB.BLM + 1 records. Alternatively, shifting
1242:				; the number of blocks by DPB.BSH gives the number of records.
